Question: Each image contains a dog with black spots on white fur, and the large spotted dog is in a reclining pose near a french bulldog in one image.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/J5AFCr00wFg/hqdefault.jpg

Right image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Q4TXvcGET94/maxresdefault.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a dog with black spots on white fur in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a dog with black spots on white fur in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the large spotted dog in a reclining pose?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the large spotted dog in a reclining pose?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the french bulldog in the image?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the french bulldog in the image?')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER5}')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER6} xor {ANSWER7}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
```
